These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, eggplant
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, sailing
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is not the person eating eggplant##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | eggplant   | broccoli  |
| Sport   | cricket | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: spinach, plum
2 different pets are kept: lizard, hedgehog
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the lizard is not the person eating plum##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | spinach | plum      |
| Pet    | lizard  | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
