 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-6::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, folk
There are 2 different nationalities: american, thai
1. the fan trance is on the far right##1
2. the fan folk is not the american##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | trance      |
| Nationality   | thai | american |

