.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, fisherman
2 different pets are kept: fish, goldfish
1. the architect is in an odd position##4
2. the architect is not the owner of the goldfish##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | architect | fisherman |
| Pet   | fish       | goldfish       |

