.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-20::.
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, golf
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is not the owner of the lizard##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |
| Pet     | lizard | guinea-pig      |
| Sport   | golf | badminton |

 